    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\n`PklProject` files are written in Pkl but do not automatically get the filetype `pkl` like `.pkl` files.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n```\nnvim --clean\n:edit foo.pkl\n:lua print(vim.bo.filetype)\n:edit PklProject\n:lua print(vim.bo.filetype)\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n`PklProject` files are automatically marked as `pkl`.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.12.1\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nYes\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS 15.7.0\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGhostty 1.3.1\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-ghostty\n\n### Installation\n\nHomebrew",
